\Abstract

We extract genus 00 consequences of the all genera quantum HRR formula proved in PartÂ IX. This includes re-proving and generalizing the adelic characterization of genusÂ 00 quantum K-theory found in [Givental A., Tonita V., in Symplectic, Poisson, and Noncommutative Geometry, Math. Sci.
